                        </a>
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="column">
                    <p>Strengthens partnerships between families &amp; communities.</p>
                    <p>
                        <a class="ui button" href="#">
                            Share
                        </a>
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
